 semi-final direct spot\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 3000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Serbia and Lithuania play each other on day six, while Netherlands meet USA.\\u00c2 Miezis does it again Another day, another Miezis dagger.\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3003, \"end\": 3009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999237651129171, \"rank\": 7.624068588112578e-05, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3014, \"end\": 3023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.172238541245028e-15, \"text\": \"Lithuania\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuania_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3058, \"end\": 3069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999493279588, \"rank\": 4.872657541533239e-08, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"Miezis\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3087}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Defending champs Latvia's unbeaten start to the tournament appeared under major threat under a French avalanche from Franck Seguela amid deafening noise at La Concorde.\\u00c2 Seguela had appeared to give France a memorable dub after hitting a long-range jumper from the corner triggering wild scenes in the bleachers.\\u00c2 But the joy as short-lived as his foot was on the line meaning the scores were deadlocked at 20 apiece.\\u00c2 And you just knew what would happen here.\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3157, \"end\": 3163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia\", \"score\": 0.9998392201803599, \"rank\": 0.00016022152577340872, \"text\": \"Latvia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia\"}, {\"begin\": 3235, \"end\": 3241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8784867046112094, \"rank\": 0.11040819149136363, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3311, \"end\": 3318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e9gu\\u00e9la_Department\", \"score\": 0.8208345750320577, \"rank\": 0.18673218673216324, \"text\": \"Seguela\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e9gu\\u00e9la_Department\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e9gu\\u00e9la_Department\"}, {\"begin\": 3340, \"end\": 3346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999608953666, \"rank\": 3.8887264909218745e-08, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"champs\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3156}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"major threat\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"Franck Seguela\", \"from\": 3257, \"to\": 3271}, {\"ngram\": \"noise\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3292}, {\"ngram\": \"La Concorde\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3307}, {\"ngram\": \"a memorable dub\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3361}, {\"ngram\": \"a long-range jumper\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\"